    "body": "Seems you are on a magnetic drive (HDD), and doing a full sync on that takes a ton of time. Please do a fast sync from scratch and see how that goes:\n- Back up your `chaindata` folder so you don't lose any progress\n- Delete your chaindata to start from scratch\n- Run `geth --fast`\n\nIt should sync very fast.\n",
